[[div class="article"]]
[[div class="picture"]]
[[span class="heading2"]]BREAKING[[/span]]

[[image http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-9506/fog.jpg]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="words"]]
[[span class="heading"]]BREAKING[[/span]]

[[span class="coolheading"]]Fog in West Virginia Exceeds Projected Duration - All Trapped Residents Presumed Dead[[/span]]

[[span class="normalcy"]]ELKINS, WV — Regional authorities confirmed that yesterday's fog persisted for over 7 hours, far exceeding the estimated 2-3 hour duration. Emergency services report near-zero survivors among those unable to evacuate from Randolph, Pocahontas, and Webster Counties...[[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]

